  "text": "Again, this equality is not satisfied by Equation (11), which means that the modification of the method proposed by Frewer and Khujadze still accounts for the transformations y(x) = y(x) only, similar to the method proposed in [CITATION_1] . In fact, when the additional constrains are accounted for, Frewer and Khujadze obtain the same set of six symmetries, as derived with the analysis proposed in [CITATION_2] .",
